{
  "stem": "4184.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's the one that sent me originally to the Ose home-- this woman, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Grunewalt. ?] And I wrote to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I ask her if I please could come to her, that I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a funny place, and I don't want to stay here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she immediately sent me money and a pass.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because you had to have passes to go from one county to the next.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she's says, get on the bus and come here, which I did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I stayed in Limoges with her for a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then she sent me to another home she felt would be better for me, because there were children my age-- you know, young people my age.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was Chateau [? de ?] [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Chabon. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No more, uh uh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never heard anything about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just like-- I just can't explain what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I know, I wanted to get away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't get away fast enough from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I ended up in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Chabon. ?] And it was a very nice home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I met people there that to this day we are friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're like my brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We get together for reunions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we're just a very close-knit bunch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And while I was in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Chabon, ?] at that point, that was in 1941, when I first came there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The director of the home asked me-- I had my sister there now, in [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Chabon. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, strictly Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had schooling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went-- we had classes every day-- every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the rest, we just-- took care of our own-- our own needs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had school every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
